  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if a dose of 40 mg dexamethasone is more effective
      as pain treatment than the currently used dose of 8 mg after arthroscopic shoulder surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
